96
00:10:18,216 --> 00:10:21,658
or alchemical herbs in the world that can be harvested.

97
00:10:22,911 --> 00:10:26,153
Intangible resources have no physical properties in the game whatsoever.

98
00:10:26,593 --> 00:10:30,515
They do not occupy space, nor do they have a particular location in the world.

99
00:10:31,176 --> 00:10:35,558
For example, once a player defeats an enemy in battle, they are rewarded with experience,

100
00:10:35,978 --> 00:10:36,799
which is intangible.

101
00:10:37,659 --> 00:10:40,421
