00:38:19,222 --> 00:38:24,326
We needed to take away some of this advantage that they had, but also maybe provide a way

470
00:38:24,386 --> 00:38:28,750
of augmenting their skills and abilities in a way that would compensate for the level

471
00:38:29,331 --> 00:38:30,832
32 content that we were going to drop on them.

