00:51:06,509 --> 00:51:07,311
mismatched armor.

620
00:51:07,795 --> 00:51:11,237
Maybe they want to get all of the dies in order to complete a full set.

621
00:51:11,257 --> 00:51:18,943
Then once they find them, it is possible to then go through along with some new technical improvements to the UI

622
00:51:18,963 --> 00:51:22,445
and actually apply these as they wish.

